snippet.title: Faani - Trailer
snippet.description:
A short game about the afterlife. Many people that have experienced Coma said that was a totally different place, the geometries were special and they haven't seen such colors before. This game is my notion about how it looks. Who knows, maybe it is.
Available in:
https://jashgames.itch.io/Faani
